---
title: Bacon & Cherry Tomato Risotto with Basil, Parmesan & Pine Nuts
description: This flavour-packed risotto literally works its magic in the oven. Using classic and simple flavours we all know and love, it's a
recipe that never fails to please.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bacon-spinach-risotto-0ee8ef68.jpg
